q 0.7 G 1 w 50 725 m 562 725 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 690 Td (Depression is more than just feeling sad. It's a real medical condition that) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 672 Td (affects how you think, feel, and handle daily activities.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 640 Td (It's like your brain's 'mood thermostat' gets stuck on low.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 610 Td (Signs that you might be dealing with depression:) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 60 572 490 22 re f Q
