BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 171.6 740 Td (THE MOOD-ACTIVITY CONNECTION) Tj ET
q 0.7 G 1 w 50 725 m 562 725 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 690 Td (Here's something scientists have discovered about depression:) Tj ET
q 0.9 g 50 645 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 665 Td (When you're depressed, you stop doing things.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 650 Td (When you stop doing things, you get more depressed. It's a cycle.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 615 Td (The good news? You can break this cycle by GENTLY adding activities) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 597 Td (back into your life - even tiny ones.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 565 Td (This is called BEHAVIORAL ACTIVATION. It works like this:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 70 540 Td (1. You do a small activity \(even if you don't feel like it\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 70 520 Td (2. Your brain gets a tiny boost of feel-good chemicals) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 70 500 Td (3. You feel slightly better \(even 1% counts!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 70 480 Td (4. That makes the next activity a little easier) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 440 Td (Track your mood before and after an activity this week:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 415 Td (Activity:) Tj ET
q 0 G 0.5 w 120 415 m 400 415 l S Q
