BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 162.0 740 Td (THOUGHT PATTERNS IN DEPRESSION) Tj ET
q 0.7 G 1 w 50 725 m 562 725 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 695 Td (Depression doesn't just affect your mood - it changes how you THINK.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 675 Td (These are called 'cognitive distortions' - thinking traps that feel real) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 655 Td (but are actually your depression talking.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 50 610 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 630 Td (ALL-OR-NOTHING THINKING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 60 615 Td (Seeing things in black and white: 'I failed one test = I'm a total failure') Tj ET
q 0.92 g 50 565 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 585 Td (CATASTROPHIZING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 60 570 Td (Assuming the worst: 'My friend didn't text back = they hate me') Tj ET
q 0.92 g 50 520 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 540 Td (MENTAL FILTER) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 60 525 Td (Only seeing the negative: 'I got 9 compliments but focus on 1 criticism') Tj ET
q 0.92 g 50 475 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 495 Td (MIND READING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 60 480 Td (Assuming you know what others think: 'Everyone thinks I'm weird') Tj ET
q 0.92 g 50 430 512 35 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 60 450 Td (SHOULD STATEMENTS) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 60 435 Td ('I should be happy' 'I should be over this by now' - adding guilt to pain) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 12 Tf 50 395 Td (Which of these thinking traps do you fall into most often?) Tj ET
q 0 G 0.5 w 50 375 m 562 375 l S Q
